HEADWORD: Prepossessing
<hw>Pre`pos*sess"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Tending to
invite favor; attracting confidence, favor, esteem, or love; attractive;
<as>as, a <ex>prepossessing</ex> manner</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Pre`pos*sess"ing*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

